text: Besjana Reçica (born 13 April 1996) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Reçica has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
